{"tid":1136660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【IG淪陷】黃心穎胞姊與網民開火 心妙：不喜歡就不要來看","createTime":"2019-05-03T07:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T22:39:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2517e2b5abb3f0245e0b4a697d56e26f4454e353","tid":1136660,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"黃心穎搭上天后老公許志安爆出「安心偷食」，事件曝光後，安仔即日出來爆喊認錯開記者會，而黃心穎出聲明道歉後，日前則秘走美國。事件不斷發酵，雖禍不及家人，但因為黃心穎把Instagram關閉留言功能，於是網友到轉到她的胞姊黃心美和黃心妙的社交網大罵，令家姐無故被拖落水。<br />\n心妙昨日雖標題「請不要轉發」貼文，她抒發心中感受：「我們活在一個充滿語言暴力的年代，很多人都認為他們可以做這種精神上和心理上侵犯別人的行為，大家都化身為判官，選擇以暴易暴，我們的世界真的生病了。」（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GQkoiy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GQkoiy&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=c9d80b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GQkoiy</a> ）結果事後網友卻不屑留言大罵：「如果你的婚姻有第三者，你會唔會仲覺得你妹冇錯&hellip;」<br />\n心妙見到被網友留言指控，她更用「強姦論」反駁對方：「是你覺得在強姦的時候我說不要，其實我是騙你一樣懂嗎？我的IG不可以發感受？謝謝你的關注 那也是我不需要的。」<br />\n當中火藥味甚濃，黃心妙再反擊網民：「我是我，針對我個人說話，你怎麼看這件事是你的自由，你精神批判，就咬定我也做同樣的事情也隨你，大家都在對號入座，我不干預別人評論別人，但來語言暴力我就不必了。」<br />\n心妙希望自己也有私人空間：「你們到哪裏評論說甚麼都可以，我的page有關心和支持我的人，人大了，沒空間留給其他的，你們的觀點與角度我都懂，人各有自，不喜歡就不要來看，來罵也沒用的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190503/large/1556861786_3608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190503%2Flarge%2F1556861786_3608.jpg&h=63be3e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190503/59558504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558504&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=0762004c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558504&h=0c023df5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190503/59558504</a>"},{"pid":"e1fdc9fb6e43553d41cc2e8e3b879db89a47876c","tid":1136660,"uid":226216,"like":189,"dislike":3,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"塊面好長"},{"pid":"ef3367940bac9b428edcc44c4ff5ca8d1799ddd8","tid":1136660,"uid":96,"like":369,"dislike":9,"score":360,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"成家都以為自己笑得好靚 死都要擺個笑到好燦爛嘅樣出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d370a194dfca8ca2cad4078076d747286b416bc","tid":1136660,"uid":94465,"like":155,"dislike":3,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"幾姊妹浸港女味重到呢⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e9625a7033226b94b669d030309623506bdcb9e5","tid":1136660,"uid":237788,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"係p圖過度定整過容嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塊臉咁膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f3f049240caaae02964dc45147b482a14beea2","tid":1136660,"uid":8410,"like":125,"dislike":5,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你地家族全部都係狐狸精， 唔想見到自己d醜事就dis activate 所有socialmedia 啦"},{"pid":"15ac0b28cf1f476c4b68bbcfac9ac00f65b2b381","tid":1136660,"uid":31540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"好柒"},{"pid":"b35e0ae30288568400797fe7a2a58c9476ec8860","tid":1136660,"uid":10637,"like":93,"dislike":2,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"最憎成日推佢3個小朋友出黎<br />\n又唔係可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最細果個前額無頭髮咁"},{"pid":"809d300d1de866580e27586a315d9309691dd584","tid":1136660,"uid":196924,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"以外國回流既家庭黎講<br />\n佢呢家人都算最柒"},{"pid":"44484dda777f5b31ec2bab108f17756